name: Gift Package
description: When used, a random player in your match will get a random item as a gift from you.

name: Pallet of Presents
description: When used, up to 9 other players in your match will get a random item as a gift from you.

name: Audience Participation Parcel
description: When used, up to 25 viewers watching your match will get a random item as a gift from you.

name: X-Ray P250 Package
description: This package contains a single custom painted P250 showing its internals with an X-Ray. P250 is a low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, which is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents.

name: Rio 2022 Storage Unit with Paper Stickers
description: This is a Storage Unit containing every Paper player autograph and every Paper sticker commemorating IEM Rio 2022 CS:GO Major Championship.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this capsule support the included players and organizations.

name: Rio 2022 Storage Unit with Glitter Stickers
description: This is a Storage Unit containing every Glitter player autograph and every Glitter sticker commemorating IEM Rio 2022 CS:GO Major Championship.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this capsule support the included players and organizations.
